{"tid":984933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【係愛呀哈利】職安真漢子！壞車塞粉公　地盤工「出力」救援","createTime":"2019-01-17T07:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T07:55:54.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3b1385f15374b257aa78b006233829279fe7bb01","tid":984933,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:55:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>職安真漢子！壞車塞粉公　地盤工「出力」救援</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117125250148-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117125250148-0117_00822_001.html&d=b1OF%2B0C98ImIiU9%2BlqVqRgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7ab58d15\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117125250148-0117_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/photo/bkn-20190117125250148-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190117131946\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190117125250148-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190117131946&h=1202d857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係愛呀！<br />\n<br />\nLINK有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc728e00ebecf5a5e40c0549e9f7589950a711c","tid":984933,"uid":225464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"年輕人，係咩驅使你喺馬路推車？係愛呀！近日有貨Van懷疑在粉嶺公路故障，有數名地盤工人即時熱心幫忙，將車輛推行逾百米至地盤整修區域，獲網民大讚︰「職安真漢子」。<br />\n<br />\n片段於星期三（16日）上傳至Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」，可見有貨Van疑死火，停在粉嶺公路慢線。當時正有道路工程，僅餘三線行車，有三名身穿反光衣的工友見狀，即時伸出援手。<br />\n<br />\n他們與附近的警員合力，推行車輛約一分鐘，並將貨Van推進至地盤圍封的區域，避免壞車造成阻塞。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛稱讚工友︰「地盤工人其實比辦公室白領更有人情味」、「冒生命危險㗎&hellip;一陣有盲毛收唔切就成班車尾係咁先&hellip;讚」、「仗義每多屠狗輩」。"}]}